 it and most of the regions of Egypt are sown by this, and it wanes by no jot, unlike it does in Iraq or Syria."}]}]}, "etymology": null, "ipa": null, "lanes_definition": {"source": "lanes", "entries": [{"entry_id": "n30327", "headword_ar": "عِلْكٌ", "root": "Elk", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Resin;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a certain thing that is chewed;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, O;) the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Samog", "text_ar": "صَمْغ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "resin"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Sanawobar", "text_ar": "صَنَوْبَر"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^arozap", "text_ar": "اَرْزَة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fusotuq", "text_ar": "فُسْتُق"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sarow", "text_ar": "سَرْو"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yanobuwt", "text_ar": "يَنْبُوت"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "buTom", "text_ar": "بُطْم"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; the last of which is the best of these; (K, TA;)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "like"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "lubaAn", "text_ar": "لُبَان"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "frankincense"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "],"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "which is chewed and is not thereby liquefied;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA;)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "heating, diuretic, and strengthening to the venereal faculty;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K, TA;)"}, {"kind": "